✅ **OpenClaw 2026.2.17** — dependencies refresh (666 packages changed)

**Nové features v poslednom OpenClaw release:**
- **Anthropic:** 1M context beta support (Opus/Sonnet)
- **iOS:** Share extension, background Talk Mode
- **Cron:** Webhook delivery, telemetry logs
- **Subagents:** Lepší context management
- **Memory:** FTS fallback s query expansion

Všetko beží hladko. 

